Class SyntaxGeneratorContainer

  • com.github.mibac138.argparser.binder.SyntaxGeneratorContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SyntaxGenerator

    public class SyntaxGeneratorContainer
implements SyntaxGenerator

    Syntax generator consisting of other generators. Does nothing on it's own. When running generate it invokes all of the added generators.
